\n到三十幾歲儲夠錢就開始正左踏上呢條路..."},{"pid":"b217b326922adace3445e0697edfd3a32946eb1b","tid":191020,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:41:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都唔知想點<br />\n又無興趣<br />\n又無長處<br />\n真係唔知點解仲要生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n想點又點 又可以點<br />\n<br />\n我以前都好多想...<br />\n<br />\n想入cu hku心理學<br />\n<br />\n想成為一個硬淨 識得同人相處既人<br />\n<br />\n點知最後書讀唔成仲要自己痴埋線<br />\n<br />\n興趣我以前好鍾意睇書<br />\n<br />\n不過近一兩年真係睇書都集中唔到<br />\n<br />\n可能因為個人諗野越黎越亂<br />\n<br />\n長處我都冇<br />\n<br />\n唔通打字快叫長處之後做成世?<br />\n<br />\n呢個世界總要有我呢d廢人<br />\n<br />\n如果人人都心想事成咁就天下大亂"},{"pid":"70952b144babae447cc8c067bedee591c0a54883","tid":191020,"uid":79353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:42:21.000Z","msg":"好懷疑自己腦部發育有問題<br />\n<br />\nIQ唔撚過60<br />\n<br />\n屌"},{"pid":"7485856847f737615f7e79ad980010e3038469c3","tid":191020,"uid":42766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:44:43.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就22  無長處 咩都唔識    好驚自己三十歲都仲係揾緊萬幾蚊一個月"},{"pid":"a6ff24b4cbb31e469bd1298f0eb44857ce70953f","tid":191020,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:44:54.000Z","msg":"agger 之前理想係入u<br />\n讀完u就唔知自己有咩目標了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買樓又知自己買唔起"},{"pid":"1c8047efc2e21ca358acce0afac2449ef7fb409a","tid":191020,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-07T14:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  就22  無長處 咩都唔識    好驚自己三十歲都仲係揾緊萬幾蚊一個月</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /